document.full_text: eman al-obeidy, the libyan women who burst into a tripoli hotel filled with journalists in late march and described a brutal rape by forces loyal to col. muammar el-qaddafi, fled to tunisia on thursday night, cnn reports.
document.title: the lede: libyan woman who claimed rape flees to tunisia
